All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Controller
The Controller class connects the model (logic) with the view (GUI)
Crop
The Crop class contains records related to the crop planted on a tile.
CropType
The CropType class is an enumeration of the crop types.
Driver
The Driver class runs the main of MyFarm.
Farmer
The Farmer class contains records related to the farmer such as wallet and level.
FarmerType
The FarmerType class is an enumeration of the registration statuses of the farmer.
MyFarm
The MyFarm class contains all records relating to all the other classes.
MyFarmGUI
The MyFarmGUI class serves as the view of the program
Tile
The Tile class contains records related to each tile in the plot.
